Speaker 2: Therefore, if you do want to try these and you like these, which I know you will,

Speaker 2: And I can guarantee you these, they're going to work better for you.

Speaker 1: You're not going to have a headache.

Speaker 2: And you're going to see the improvement on these particular ones.

Speaker 1: Can I go ahead and do that for you?

Speaker 2: I'm sorry?

Speaker 1: No, sir.

Speaker 2: No, sir.

Speaker 1: No, I don't want to take the chance.

Speaker 2: No.

Speaker 1: All right.

Speaker 2: Not a problem.

Speaker 1: Like I said, I just wanted to give you an opportunity to try them.

Speaker 2: These were the new and improved Viagra pills that I wanted to send you.

Speaker 1: That's why I wanted to do it for you.

Speaker 2: Appreciate that.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: Yep.

Speaker 1: No.

Speaker 1: Not a problem.

Speaker 2: you wouldn't be able to because you actually are canceling the prescription that I'm trying to set you up for

Speaker 1: before it even gets started.

Speaker 2: Got it.

Speaker 1: Okay?

Speaker 2: I understand.

Speaker 1: Yes, sir.

Speaker 1: Not a problem.

Speaker 2: Not a problem there, Mr. Evans.

Speaker 1: Okay?
